<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 05:18:48 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>布卢明顿超跑夜景</title><link>https://some.pics/6a24ff352ba97</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在明尼苏达州布卢明顿举行的FANS超级跑步活动的夜晚景色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A serene evening scene showing a lake reflecting the darkening sky. Silhouetted trees and buildings line the horizon, with a faint glow from city lights. The sky transitions from dark blue to orange near the horizon." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a24ff352ba97.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 05:18:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>周六夜编程</title><link>https://some.pics/6a24da81d9d1d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;周六晚上编程&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="coding at saturday night" height="5304" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pmurad/6a24da81d9d1d.jpg" width="7952"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pmurad.some.pics"&gt;@pmurad&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 02:42:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>画布的背面</title><link>https://some.pics/6a24b39731211</link><description>&lt;p&gt;画布的背面。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The back of a canvas frame displaying a Certificate of Authenticity from Art Brand Studios. The certificate features a hand-drawn, colored sketch of Phineas the Hitchhiking Ghost, an artist's signature, the year 2026, and a holographic &amp;quot;Genuine&amp;quot; sticker." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a24b39731211.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 23:56:10 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a24af056bffc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;扎克·金凯德的幽灵公馆&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A vibrant painting of Disney's Haunted Mansion graveyard scene. The foreground features the three Hitchhiking Ghosts, along with the frightened caretaker and his dog riding in a horse-drawn hearse. The background shows the haunted mansion, various transparent ghosts among the tombstones, and Madame Leota's face glowing within a full moon." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a24af056bffc.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 23:36:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Podmander部署成功</title><link>https://some.pics/6a247feb1b3a7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;成功的Podmander部署：左上角是中央控制器，右上角是节点代理，底部是podctl命令行界面。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Successful Podmander deployment: Top left the central controller, top right the node agent, bottom the podctl CLI" height="928" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/geewiz/6a247feb1b3a7.png" width="2548"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://geewiz.some.pics"&gt;@geewiz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 20:15:41 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>